  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package re-evaluates COU1 under an elevated Model Risk Level 5 designation following expanded regulatory scrutiny of Class II CPB devices. Several credibility factors remain not-assessed despite the elevated risk level; no documented justification for the gaps is provided in the decision record.",
